8. COPYRIGHT NOTICE

This software discovers and indexes metadata about files shared on public 
peer-to-peer networks. The software:
- Does NOT host, store, or distribute copyrighted content
- Does NOT provide direct downloads of any content
- Only indexes publicly available metadata (file names, hashes, etc.)
- Cannot control what content exists on peer-to-peer networks

The presence of a torrent in this index does not imply that:
- The content is legal to download in your jurisdiction
- The content is free from copyright protection
- The authors endorse or recommend downloading the content

